Dungeon Save & Load - Assignment 2

This project implements dungeon generation with save and load functionality for assignment 2. 
The dungeon is randomly generated with rooms, corridors, and stairs. 
The player can save the dungeon and load it later.

How to compile and run:
Compile the project using:
make
Run the game:
   ./dungeon

saving and loading:
To generate and save a dungeon:
./dungeon --save

To load a previously saved dungeon: 
./dungeon --load

The dungeon is saved in:
~/.rlg327/dungeon

to remove compiled files use:
make clean